      "raw_text": "WALLACE, March 2S.-Paul\nEmmanuelson was taken uninjured\nfrom the Bunker Hill mine last\nnight after being imprisoned by a\ncavein for % hours. Rasmussen,\nhis partner, who was found nearer\nthe entrance Yesterday, aided in\nthe second rescue. The party\ndrove drift II feet by hand in\norder to reach Emmanuelson. The\nmen were caught while timbering\ncaving ground."
